data.description:
PRICE ADJUSTMENT, Buyer agent commission increase, AND $5,000 Seller incentive! Welcome to 9076 Prolonge Lane. An amazing home tucked away in a gorgeous cul-de-sac with over 4,000 square feet. As you step into your breathtaking foyer with phenomenal lighting and, what seems like, sky high ceilings you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living area, featuring large windows that flood the space with natural light. First floor primary with huge en-suite, half bath and laundry room. The first floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area, creating a space for entertaining guests.
Venturing upstairs, you'll find a functional landing space and 4 spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms.And surprise surprise…. There’s a second primary space on the third level! It features a spacious bedroom area, with ample closet space and plenty of storage. There’s also a living area and efficient kitchen. Outside, the property boasts a well-maintained backyard, providing a serene retreat for outdoor activities or relaxation.Commuting is a breeze with easy access to major highways. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning home yours!
